ZH: 我们需要给专家的演讲做一个评价。
EN: We need to evaluate the expert's presentation.

ZH: 这本书的评价很高。
EN: The book received high praise.

ZH: 他对我的工作态度进行了评价。
EN: He evaluated my work attitude.

ZH: 请您给这家餐厅的服务做个评价。
EN: Please evaluate the service of this restaurant.

ZH: 他在比赛中获得了极佳的评价。
EN: He received excellent reviews in the competition.

ZH: 无法只根据外表来评价一个人。
EN: You can't judge a person solely based on appearances.

ZH: 学生们在课堂上被要求相互评价。
EN: Students were asked to evaluate each other in class.

ZH: 她的演技得到了很高的评价。
EN: Her acting skills received high praise.

ZH: 质量检验员对产品进行了评价。
EN: The quality inspector evaluated the products.

ZH: 陪审团将对被告进行评价。
EN: The jury will evaluate the defendant.

ZH: 这种药物的副作用需要进行评价。
EN: The side effects of this medication need to be evaluated.

ZH: 我们需要对这项计划做出合理的评价。
EN: We need to make a rational assessment of this plan.

ZH: 专家们对这一决定的评价不一。
EN: Experts have different opinions on this decision.

ZH: 我们要对现有的政策进行评价。
EN: We need to evaluate the existing policies.

ZH: 老板给员工的完成任务的评价很高。
EN: The boss gave high praise to the employees for completing the tasks.

ZH: 运动员表现出色，得到了评价。
EN: The athlete performed well and received praise.

ZH: 听众对这场演讲的评价是积极的。
EN: The audience's feedback on the speech was positive.

ZH: 学校需要对学生的学术成绩进行定期评价。
EN: The school needs to regularly evaluate the students' academic performance.

ZH: 这位艺术家获得了良好的评价。
EN: The artist received good reviews.

ZH: 环保组织负责对环境进行评价。
EN: The environmental organization is responsible for evaluating the environment.
